{"title":"建筑工人赞歌","authors":["王晓辉"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":4,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"建筑工人赞歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王晓辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用粗糙的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织着襁褓的护网"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用粗糙的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"架起钢管搭成的摇篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妊娠中的阵痛呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸣奏工地的交响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临盆中的呻吟呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊动着四邻街坊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水中，我总是把你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"降生在坚实的地基上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨中，你在我的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵护下茁壮成长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱掉襁褓吧——孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你已长成剽悍的新郎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拆掉摇篮吧——孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你更像待嫁的新娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成人后的欣慰，转瞬间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又变成骨肉分离的惆怅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪水已刷净汗渍的工装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再见吧，我已长大的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离别才能孕育新的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘带走的只是手上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新添的老茧，还有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分娩时留下的创伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再见吧，已出嫁的新娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是我留给地平线上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一曲凝固的英雄乐章"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}